{"about_the_game":"A sunshiny, summer-time, and picturesque logic mind-teaser.\u00a0But summer cannot last forever.\u00a0Help the Chipmunk stock up on seeds and nuts for the very cold incoming winter.<br>Plunge into an interesting adventure passing the forest worlds through lots of levels of varying difficulty.\u00a0Put to a good use the balls and bricks; plan your actions in advance.\u00a0This is not easy, because monsters and traps that must be overcome to get to the nut at the other end of the level will hinder you<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>\u25cf Well-thought-out levels that will stick in your memory<br>\u25cf Beautiful pixel art.\u00a0Forest, rivers, and animals<br>\u25cf Relaxing music and sound effects<br>\u25cf Plan your actions a few steps ahead<br>\u25cf There is no time limit.\u00a0Take your time and think as much as you like<br>\u25cf Hints on the most disobedient levels<br>\u25cf Several hours of fun and interesting gameplay<br><br>Competent planning of your further moves will help you gain gaming experience for the follow-up action in more complicated puzzles and will make you think hard<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063300/extras/Steam_gif_normal_7_1.gif?t=1603305296\" /><br>Think over different puzzles, try various options for passing, and do not be afraid to experiment<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063300/extras/Steam_gif_hard_3_3.gif?t=1603305296\" /><br>3 Worlds with increasing complexity of logic\u00a0puzzles, where thinking and passing through the game can take a lot of time<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063300/extras/Steam_gif_normal_12.gif?t=1603305296\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Crusher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1063300/f508d24a0082b9730cb3fcc1d0398970b5ae0603